      "description": "The Intech S&P Small-Mid Cap Diversified Alpha ETF (SMDX) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in extended market equity. The fund is an actively managed fund of US small- to mid-cap companies found in the S&P 1000 Index. It utilizes volatility, correlation, profitability, and valuations to identify and select stocks. SMDX was launched on Feb 27, 2025 and is issued by Intech ETFs.",
